{"tid":327884,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"超速兼行車證過期 尹兆堅被罰900元","createTime":"2017-07-19T06:39:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-19T06:50:52.000Z","uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0410d7b47d9ff1e5887eabce0f9a440240cd656d","tid":327884,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T06:39:49.000Z","msg":"民主黨立法會議員尹兆堅於去年12月3日，在屯門公路近屯興路以時速92公里駕車，<span style=\"color: red;\">超速22公里</span>，警方調查發現<span style=\"color: red;\">尹的行車證過期</span>。尹被票控兩罪，案件原定今天於屯門法院進行答辯，惟尹已於較早前以書面方式認罪，沒現身法庭下被判定額罰款共900元。<br />\n<br />\n尹兆堅表示，他的車有買足保險，但因太忙忘記續牌，至警察通知才知悉，現在需先維修及驗車，有驗車紙便可續行車證。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170718&amp;guid=56972253&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170718%26guid%3D56972253%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant&d=ntfgr0TBCPsu0edoeYNYOQhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=8c88863e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170718%26guid%3D56972253%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant&h=6f737b12\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170718&amp;guid=56972253&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"bffd4d623b637695d55f19483be213435b7a3359","tid":327884,"uid":37197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T06:47:20.000Z","msg":"好撚憎依個肥西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b827caaaf703888753176627e4908f169cb4d372","tid":327884,"uid":61105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T06:49:51.000Z","msg":"唔怪得屯公成日交通意外搞到塞車啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3af5c6a401e4dbab168f762140cea6980693639c","tid":327884,"uid":61653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T06:50:52.000Z","msg":"通常班賤民罰幾多？"}]}